    "In line 5, we utilize the VPG-C architecture [24] to enhance semantic alignment by reextracting the visual contents in the medium layer of the LLM.",
    "In line 6, we implement the training pipeline proposed in MMICL [51], which involves joint training of the projection layer and the query and value vectors.",
    "To maintain consistent training parameters, we limit the training to the query and value vectors in the first two attention layers of the LLM.",
